# {{qualifier|of people and things}} [[little]] [[known]], [[unfamiliar]] {{gloss|previously encountered but not familiar or well-acquainted}}; [[unrecognized]], [[unfamiliar]], [[unidentified]] {{gloss|previously encountered but not known by name or identity}}
#: {{syn|fr|ignoré|[[peu]] [[connu]]}}
#: {{ux|fr|Elle habite une maison modeste dans un quartier '''méconnu''' de son amant.|She lives in a modest house in an area '''unfamiliar''' to her lover.}}
# {{qualifier|of people and things}} [[misunderstood]] {{gloss|which is correctly recognized or identified, but whose true nature, qualities, character, etc. are not}}
#: {{syn|fr|incompris|[[mal]] [[connu]]}}
# {{qualifier|of people and things}} [[underappreciated]], [[unrecognized]] {{gloss|deserving or worthy of recognition that is not received}}
#: {{syn|fr|sous-estimé}}
