====Usage notes====
* The word '''{{m|fr||méconnu}}''' refers to someone or something that has been encountered but is not entirely familiar; a related term, {{m|fr|inconnu}}, refers to someone or something not previously encountered and totally unknown.<ref>{{cite-web|fr|url=https://blog.alorthographe.com/2016/09/20/inconnu-et-meconnu/ |title=Inconnu et méconnu {{!}} Blog alorthographe |accessdate=23 June 2022 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210928140010/http://blog.alorthographe.com/2016/09/20/inconnu-et-meconnu/ |archivedate=28 September 2021 }}</ref><ref>[https://hinative.com/en-US/questions/14888325 What is the difference between "inconnu" and "méconnu" ? "inconnu" vs "méconnu" ? | HiNative]</ref>
